# React - Fernando Herrera Course (Udemy)

This repository contains the projects and exercises developed during the **React** course taught by [Fernando Herrera](https://www.udemy.com/user/fernando-herrera/) on Udemy.
The goal is to learn the fundamentals of React and its modern tools for web application development.

